comments.comment: Asked Johnny what furniture he would like more immediate and what can wait. He asked the bedroom furniture to be last. Everything else can be delivered first. He said if we can fit the primary bedroom, great, if not no worries. Definitely guest bedroom items can be next trip. Those spaces are currently being used as storage.  -JC

Spoke with Johnny per Art. Let him know that we would need to do two separate trips. We will bring one truckload of furniture down and store it in his residence. Shortly after we will schedule a second trip with the second load and we will finish installation. This is a single family home in a gated community. There are limitations to this community in terms of their hours. Mon-Fri: 8am-5pm. And Saturday 8am-12pm. All trucks/ service vehicles must be outside of the community gate by end of allowed time. Relayed this to Art.  -JC

The customer's home renovations will be complete by the December 20th. He is available to for delivery after that date. He asked about the possibility of shipping his lighting fedex so the contractors can install it. -RH
